    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186180/extras/986e5af3908c3906b9cdfcd610299c54.webp?t=1753962366\" width=678 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186180/extras/5daf9aceb55b423becb7feea33c08f5b.poster.avif?t=1753962366\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186180/extras/5daf9aceb55b423becb7feea33c08f5b.webm?t=1753962366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186180/extras/5daf9aceb55b423becb7feea33c08f5b.mp4?t=1753962366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在墙壁上疾行、追赶对手，像真正的忍者一样利用各种物品解决对方——武士刀、苦无、锤子，甚至还有平底锅！被人解决，惨败出局？没关系，即刻返回游戏惩罚那个家伙：这里没有无聊的等待！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186180/extras/8c6829536134fc30cd74529c58f811ed.webp?t=1753962366\" width=678 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186180/extras/333abb0573b441eb16de81694277c3c4.poster.avif?t=1753962366\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186180/extras/333abb0573b441eb16de81694277c3c4.webm?t=1753962366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186180/extras/333abb0573b441eb16de81694277c3c4.mp4?t=1753962366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在12名挑战者中撑到最后，摘下最强忍者的桂冠。在各种模式中完成一个个挑战，体会真正的忍者派对大逃杀体验。随着各个阶段推进，对手会逐渐出局，最终只有一个赢家！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186180/extras/95f390455d5bae2e79dbfc5b4e443240.webp?t=1753962366\" width=678 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186180/extras/3319e0362df3efa7e9c7f0b7d8cc12f0.poster.avif?t=1753962366\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186180/extras/3319e0362df3efa7e9c7f0b7d8cc12f0.webm?t=1753962366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186180/extras/3319e0362df3efa7e9c7f0b7d8cc12f0.mp4?t=1753962366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与一名朋友组队，带领你的小小忍者氏族走向胜利。与朋友相互掩护，一起成为最强忍者！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186180/extras/8cd74ad4b3a979a661625fd094bbee7f.webp?t=1753962366\" width=678 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186180/extras/1f785e52589c87c9a786bdf6a3179304.poster.avif?t=1753962366\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186180/extras/1f785e52589c87c9a786bdf6a3179304.webm?t=1753962366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186180/extras/1f785e52589c87c9a786bdf6a3179304.mp4?t=1753962366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进行游戏即可填补皮肤收藏并升级你最爱的皮肤——让它们的外观更上一层楼。组建你的忍者收藏吧！</p>",
